casebody.data:
Teddy MOORE, Appellant,
v.
Frank GUERRA, Defendant, City of New York, et al., Respondents. Motion No: 2018-42 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided March 27, 2018

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.

Motion for poor person relief etc. dismissed as academic.
